com.yundotech.mymvp.model

接口 IBaseModel<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the data's class for model, which has all the fields of one certain database's table

    public interface IBaseModel<T>
    Interface definition template for Model

    • 方法详细资料

      • addListener

        void addListener(com.yundotech.mymvp.model.IBaseModelListener listener)
        the presenter should implement IBaseModelListener and call this function of each model.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        参数:
        listener - the operation listener of this model

      • removeListener

        void removeListener(com.yundotech.mymvp.model.IBaseModelListener listener)
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        参数:
        listener - the operation listener of this model

      • fetchList

        boolean fetchList()
        to fetch a list of all data from server.
        Note: sub-class of BasePresenter will call it while updating list.
        返回:
        true for fetching request is sent successfully, or else false

      • addNewOne

        boolean addNewOne(java.lang.Object one)
        to save a new item to server.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        参数:
        one - the data to add whose class type must be the model's T type
        返回:
        true for adding request is sent successfully, or else false

      • modifyOne

        boolean modifyOne(java.lang.Object one)
        to modify a certain item in server.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        参数:
        one - the data to modify whose class type must be the model's T type
        返回:
        true for modifying request is sent successfully, or else false

      • deleteOne

        boolean deleteOne(java.lang.Object one)
        to delete a certain item in server.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        参数:
        one - the data to add whose class type must be the model's T type
        返回:
        true for deleting request is sent successfully, or else false

      • setFilters

        boolean setFilters(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> filters)
        to fetch data list by some filters.
        参数:
        filters - a map to store filters, which will be add to the URL as parameters
        返回:
        true for fetching request with filters is sent successfully, or else false

      • clearFilters

        boolean clearFilters()
        to clear filters and fetch a list of all data
        返回:
        true for fetching request without filters is sent successfully, or else false

      • getList

        java.util.ArrayList<T> getList()
        to get current data list.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        返回:
        an array list of all data

      • getDataType

        java.lang.reflect.Type getDataType()
        to get data's class type in this model.
        Note: It's called in BasePresenter, and no need to call it in sub-class of BasePresenter.
        返回:
        the class type of this model's data
